overview: Develop Your Psychic Powers purports that "your psychic abilities are a basic part of you," and clairvoyant Litany Burns wants to help you discover and use your "own natural psychic talents." Speaking in a soothing tone, she explains exercises you can practice with the video and on your own while others in the video demonstrate.
tagline: Learn how to develop your own Psychic Talents with world-famous Medium and Clairvoyant Litany Burns
title: Develop Your Psychic Powers
